{
  "text": "Meat products were not statistically associated with HEV seropositivity but showed higher rates (>55%) (game, offal, liver, pork). These meat products have been frequently associated with higher seroprevalence or HEV RNA detection [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
